  "ai_usage": "Use for playful brands, kids, festivals, and creative studios. The recipe: cream canvas, bold primaries, thick black outlines, and a scatter of geometric 'confetti' (dots, squiggles, triangles, arches) behind chunky type — built as CSS shapes. Mark shapes aria-hidden, keep text on solid blocks for contrast, and stop the float under reduced motion.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/memphis-playful.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Memphis Style — Playful Brand</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"memphis-playful\",\n  \"title\": \"Memphis Style — Playful Brand\",\n  \"summary\": \"An 80s-Memphis brand page: primary colors on cream, scattered geometric confetti (squiggles, circles, triangles, zig-zags) with bold black outlines.\",\n  \"description\": \"The Memphis Group aesthetic — bold primaries, black outlines, and a confetti of geometric shapes (dots, squiggles, triangles, arches) floating behind chunky type. Playful and energetic; great for kids' brands, festivals, creative studios, and events.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"brand\", \"experimental\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"memphis\", \"80s\", \"geometric\", \"playful\", \"primary-colors\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers.\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"All shapes are CSS (borders/gradients/clip-paths); a gentle float on a few. No images. Light.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Decorative shapes are aria-hidden; text keeps strong contrast on solid blocks; real buttons/links with focus-visible. Float stops under reduced-motion.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"--red/--blue/--yellow\", \"description\": \"Memphis primaries\", \"default\": \"coral/cobalt/lemon\" },\n    { \"name\": \"shape positions\", \"description\": \"Scatter of confetti\", \"default\": \"edit markup\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Pastel-Memphis palette\", \"Add terrazzo speckle texture\", \"Squiggle dividers between sections\"],\n  \"related\": [\"dopamine-brand\", \"neubrutalist-landing\", \"anti-design\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for playful brands, kids, festivals, and creative studios. The recipe: cream canvas, bold primaries, thick black outlines, and a scatter of geometric 'confetti' (dots, squiggles, triangles, arches) behind chunky type — built as CSS shapes. Mark shapes aria-hidden, keep text on solid blocks for contrast, and stop the float under reduced motion.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--cream:#fdf6e3;--ink:#15140f;--red:#ff5a5f;--blue:#3a5bff;--yellow:#ffd23f;--teal:#2ec4b6;--pink:#ff6ec7;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--cream);color:var(--ink);font-family:\"Poppins\",\"Trebuchet MS\",system-ui,sans-serif;line-height:1.5;overflow-x:hidden}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  .wrap{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.4rem;position:relative;z-index:2}\n  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:78px}\n  .brand{font-weight:900;font-size:1.5rem;letter-spacing:-.02em}\n  .links{display:flex;gap:1.2rem;align-items:center;font-weight:700}\n  .btn{display:inline-block;background:var(--ink);color:var(--yellow);border:3px solid var(--ink);border-radius:999px;padding:.6rem 1.3rem;font-weight:800;cursor:pointer;box-shadow:4px 4px 0 var(--red);transition:transform .12s,box-shadow .12s}\n  .btn:hover{transform:translate(-2px,-2px);box-shadow:6px 6px 0 var(--red)}\n  .btn:active{transform:translate(2px,2px);box-shadow:1px 1px 0 var(--red)}\n  .btn.blue{box-shadow:4px 4px 0 var(--blue)}.btn.blue:hover{box-shadow:6px 6px 0 var(--blue)}\n  a:focus-visible,.btn:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--blue);outline-offset:3px}\n  .hero{position:relative;text-align:center;padding:4rem 0 5rem}\n  h1{font-size:clamp(2.8rem,9vw,6rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-.03em;line-height:.95;margin:0 0 1rem}\n  h1 .r{color:var(--red)}h1 .b{color:var(--blue)}h1 .y{background:var(--yellow);padding:0 .12em;border:3px solid var(--ink);display:inline-block;transform:rotate(-2deg)}\n  .hero p{font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:600;max-width:34ch;margin:0 auto 1.8rem}\n  .ctas{display:flex;gap:.9rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}\n  /* memphis shapes */\n  .shape{position:absolute;z-index:0;border:3px solid var(--ink)}\n  .dot{border-radius:50%}\n  .s-circle{width:70px;height:70px;background:var(--yellow);border-radius:50%;left:6%;top:18%;animation:bob 6s ease-in-out infinite}\n  .s-tri{width:0;height:0;border-left:34px solid transparent;border-right:34px solid transparent;border-bottom:60px solid var(--red);border-top:none;right:9%;top:14%;animation:spin 18s linear infinite}\n  .s-arch{width:90px;height:45px;border-bottom:none;border-radius:90px 90px 0 0;background:var(--blue);left:12%;bottom:16%;animation:bob 7s ease-in-out infinite .5s}\n  .s-zig{right:12%;bottom:18%;width:90px;height:24px;border:none;background:\n    repeating-linear-gradient(135deg,var(--teal) 0 8px,transparent 8px 16px);border-top:3px solid var(--ink);transform:rotate(-8deg)}\n  .s-dotgrid{left:46%;top:10%;width:60px;height:60px;border:none;background:radial-gradient(var(--ink) 2px,transparent 2px);background-size:14px 14px}\n  .s-sq{width:46px;height:46px;background:var(--pink);right:30%;bottom:8%;transform:rotate(12deg)}\n  @keyframes bob{50%{transform:translateY(-16px)}}\n  @keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}\n  section{padding:3.5rem 0;position:relative}\n  h2{font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-.02em;text-align:center;margin:0 0 2rem}\n  .cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.4rem}\n  .card{border:3px solid var(--ink);border-radius:20px;padding:1.6rem;box-shadow:6px 6px 0 var(--ink);background:#fff}\n  .card:nth-child(1){background:#fff}.card:nth-child(2){background:var(--yellow)}.card:nth-child(3){background:var(--teal);color:#04211d}\n  .card .ic{font-size:2rem}.card h3{margin:.4rem 0 .3rem;font-weight:900}.card p{margin:0;font-weight:600}\n  .band{background:var(--blue);color:#fff;border:3px solid var(--ink);border-radius:28px;padding:3rem 1.5rem;text-align:center;box-shadow:8px 8px 0 var(--ink)}\n  .band h2{color:#fff}\n  footer{text-align:center;padding:2.5rem 0 3rem;font-weight:700}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(22px) rotate(-1deg);transition:opacity .6s,transform .6s cubic-bezier(.2,.9,.3,1)}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  @media(max-width:820px){.cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}.links a:not(.btn){display:none}.shape{display:none}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.s-circle,.s-arch,.s-tri{animation:none}.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <nav>\n      <div class=\"brand\">◑ WIGGLE</div>\n      <div class=\"links\"><a href=\"#\">Work</a><a href=\"#\">Play</a><a href=\"#\">About</a><a class=\"btn blue\" href=\"#\">Say hi</a></div>\n    </nav>\n  </div>\n\n  <header class=\"hero\">\n    <span class=\"shape s-circle dot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    <span class=\"shape s-tri\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    <span class=\"shape s-arch\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    <span class=\"shape s-zig\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    <span class=\"shape s-dotgrid\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    <span class=\"shape s-sq\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    <div class=\"wrap\">\n      <h1>Make it <span class=\"r\">weird</span>,<br>make it <span class=\"y\">work</span>, <span class=\"b\">repeat.</span></h1>\n      <p>A creative studio for brands that refuse to be boring.</p>\n      <div class=\"ctas\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">See our play →</a><a class=\"btn blue\" href=\"#\">Start a project</a></div>\n    </div>\n  </header>\n\n  <section class=\"wrap\">\n    <h2 class=\"reveal\">What we make</h2>\n    <div class=\"cards\">\n      <div class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ic\">🎨</div><h3>Identity</h3><p>Logos and systems with serious personality.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ic\">🕹️</div><h3>Web &amp; motion</h3><p>Sites that wiggle, bounce, and convert.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ic\">📦</div><h3>Packaging</h3><p>Shelf-stopping, shareable, unmistakable.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <section class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"band reveal\">\n    <h2>Let's make something loud.</h2>\n    <p style=\"font-weight:600;max-width:38ch;margin:0 auto 1.4rem\">We take on a few wild projects a season. Yours could be next.</p>\n    <a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Book a chat →</a>\n  </div></section>\n\n  <footer>© <span id=\"yr\"></span> WIGGLE Studio · made with too much coffee &amp; primary colors</footer>\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();\n    var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(es){es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(e.target)}})},{threshold:.12});\n    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function(el){io.observe(el)});\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
